Dear teenage Ahsaas, 
Remember ALL those things you went through? Remember all that stuff you kept to yourself? Remember the problems you never spoke about because you didn’t want to be judged? I’m finally talking about them. About you. About things that every teenager goes through. It’s time for me to speak up and for you to feel heard. And it’s all happening on Dear Teenage Me, a @spotifyindia Original podcast, where me and a few others get to deep dive into our teenage anxieties like never before. It’s about to get real 🌻
- Ahsaas ✨
